header#banner.nl.hero-unit(layout="row", layout-xs="column")
  .container
    h1 About tonight ?
    span
      i.fa.fa-glass.fa-fw
      i.fa.fa-beer.fa-fw
      i.fa.fa-coffee.fa-fw
      i.fa.fa-taxi.fa-fw
div#nlBody(md-theme="default")
  #nlContainer.container
    div#nlBody(layout="row", layout-xs="column")
      div#userStory(flex="35", flex-xs="100")
        h3 User Story
        div#divider
          ul
            li As an unauthenticated user, I can view all bars in my area.

            li As an authenticated user, I can add myself to a bar to indicate I am going there tonight.

            li As an authenticated user, I can remove myself from a bar if I no longer want to go there.

            li User Story: As an unauthenticated user, when I login I should not have to search again.

      div#listVenue(flex="65" layout="column", flex-xs="100")
        form(layout layout-align="center", layout-padding)
          div(layout="row" flex)
            md-input-container.md-icon-float.md-block.md-title(flex)
              label.Search search for venues
              input(type="text", ng-model='$ctrl.searchTerms')
            div
              md-button.md-raised.md-default.md-primary(ng-Click ='$ctrl.searchVenue()', aria-label='searchForm')
                 i.fa.fa-search.fa-fw
